PrecisAppointment of JULIE M. DURETTE, of St-Hilaire, New Brunswick, as a Vice-Chairperson of the Canada Industrial Relations Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years; and order that JULIE M. DURETTE be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act; effective August 28, 2000.
